== Overview ==
The Pyroclast is another reactor which uses the magmatic principle. Unlike the standard [[Magmatic|Magmatic Reactor]] this version is absolutely massive.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Magmatic Pyroclast Reactor can be bought in the workshop after obtaining [[Magma Technology]].

